metadata.name: Portrait Of A Netrunner: Emelia
metadata.description:
Original Digital + AI Assisted Art, 3000x3000
An exploratory art study following fictitious subjects going through different stages of cyber augmentation in their transcendental journey to become one with the machine.

Emelia is a netrunner whose undergone many cybernetic augmentations she's near the peak of her journey.

About This Work:
This work was created using MidJourney and Stable Diffusion, post processing done through Photoshop and Topaz Suite.
